tags.name: Road 509
tags.note: North Frontenac municipal road 509. Formerly Secondary/Provincial Highway 509. Along Hwy 41, Ontario's signs read "North Frontenac Road 506". North Frontenac has not replaced the Secondary Highway signage along municipal roads 506 and 509.
